Package: scistreer
Title: Maximum-Likelihood Perfect Phylogeny at Scale
URL: https://github.com/kharchenkolab/scistreer
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Teng","Gao", email="tgaoteng@gmail.com", role=c("cre", "aut")), person("Evan", "Biederstedt", email="evan.biederstedt@gmail.com", role="aut"), person("Peter", "Kharchenko", email = "peter_kharchenko@hms.harvard.edu", role = "aut"), person("Yufeng", "Wu", email = "yufeng.wu@uconn.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: R/Rcpp implementation of the Single Cell Infinite Sites Tree (ScisTree) algorithm <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btz676>. It improves scalability of the algorithm via RcppParallel and is applicable to very large single-cell datasets (>10,000 cells).
